sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open workspace channels
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels
    API->>API: Validate JWT and workspace access
    API->>DB: Load workspace channels
    DB-->>API: Channel list
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + channels
    Frontend-->>User: Display channel list
